    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>anibus</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>Spenis vixit <expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>VI <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>ensibus</ex></expan> VIIII <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>iebus</ex></expan> XXIIX domi<lb break="no" n="4"/>ni et parentes Primiti<lb break="no" n="5"/>vus et Sotira dolentes <lb n="6"/>fecerunt </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Θεοῖς ∙ Καταχθονίοις <lb n="2"/>Σπῆνις ἔζησεν ἔτη <lb n="3"/>ϛʹ μῆν(ας) θʹ ἡμ(έρας) κηʹ οἱ κύρι<lb break="no" n="4"/>οι καὶ γονεῖς Πρειμιτεῖ<lb break="no" n="5"/>βος καὶ Σωτείρα πονοῦν<lb break="no" n="6"/>τες ἐποίησαν
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Wiederentdeckung des modernen Aufbewahrungsortes durch Papakonstantinou-Diamantourou (AE 1993).</p>
